<i>noun</i>: 허심탄회 [허심탄회/허심탄훼] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허심탄회 [허심탄회/허심탄훼]</dt><br>
<dd>frankness; open-mindedness</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 품은 생각을 숨김없이 말할 수 있을 만큼 아무 거리낌이 없고 솔직함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being honest without hesitation to the extent of disclosing all of one's thoughts openly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>